block body

  section.hero.is-landing.is-medium.is-success
    .hero-content
      .container

        a(href='/').is-logo
          img(src='#{assetUrl}/img/logo.png', alt='logo')

        h1.title.is-2
          strong Artificial Ingelligence
          |  for your
          strong  money.

        h2.subtitle.is-4 Your smart assistant for everyday spending.

        a(href='#').button.is-outlined.is-pill.is-wider.is-large.is-cta GET STARTED



  section.hero.is-landing-2nd.is-medium
    .hero-content
      .container
        .columns
          .column.is-6
            h1.title.is-4 Smart Savings.
            p Money.ai uses a statistical approach to compare your spending to that of the people around you.
            p Don’t worry, all data is anonymous.

          .column.is-5.is-offset-1
            img(src='#{assetUrl}/img/screen1.png', alt='smart savings')

  section.hero.is-landing-2nd.is-medium.is-bg
    .hero-content
      .container
        .columns
          .column.is-5
            img(src='#{assetUrl}/img/screen2.png', alt='smart savings')

          .column.is-6.is-offset-1
            h1.title.is-4 Smart Monitoring.
            p Money.ai keeps an eye on your bank account and credit cards. If anything seems out of your typical spending habits, we’ll check in with you.
            p Never forget to pay your credit card or rent again.

  section.hero.is-landing-2nd.is-medium
    .hero-content
      .container
        .columns
          .column.is-6
            h1.title.is-4 Smart Analysis.
            p Our machine learning algorithms build your personal revenue and expense profile and will isolate specific events like a trip, for instance.
            p This way you can really understand what’s happening with your money. Because in the end, it shouldn’t be this complicated.

          .column.is-5.is-offset-1
            img(src='#{assetUrl}/img/screen3.png', alt='smart savings')


  //- section.hero.is-landing-2nd.is-medium
    .hero-content
      .container.is-fluid

        .feature
          h1.title.is-4 Smart Savings.
          img(src='#{assetUrl}/img/screen1.png', alt='smart savings')

        .feature
          h1.title.is-4 Smart Monitoring.
          img(src='#{assetUrl}/img/screen2.png', alt='smart monitoring')

        .feature
          h1.title.is-4 Smart Analysis.
          img(src='#{assetUrl}/img/screen3.png', alt='smart analysis')


  section.hero.is-success.is-landing-cta
    .hero-content
      .container
        h1.title.is-3 Take control money of your money.
        a(href='#').button.is-pill.is-wider.is-medium.is-cta GET STARTED


  //- section.hero.is-medium.is-landing-faq
    .hero-content

      h1.title.is-4 FAQ.

      .columns
        .column.is-8.is-offset-2
          .question
            p.q Q. Is this secure?
            p.a Security is our number one priority and dictates the way we develop our product and informs every decision we make. We follow industry-standard security protocols and are constantly keeping abreast of new developments.

          .question
            p.q Q. What happens to my data?
            p.a Money.ai uses sophisticated algorithms to identify, track and categorize your spending. Our algorithms also help us make suggestions to help you save money. NO human ever looks at your data.

          .question
            p.q Q. Do you bill my card?
            p.a Money.ai is a 100% free service. We will never bill your bank account or credit cards for any service we provide. Everything is Read Only.

          p.email Got something else to tell us? email&nbsp;
            a(href='mailto:hello@money.ai') hello@money.ai
